            <h1 class="article-title">Construction Management</h1>
             <p class="display-6 article-subtitle">95% of knowledge about a construction project is lost during progress. Learn how blockchain will solve this & how Augmented & Virtual reality will optimize the cost and time required for design selection.</p>         
            <hr>
            <br>
          
        </div>

        <img class="img-responsive article-image-1" src="../../public/img-article/const 4.png" alt="dsbcjkdbvbh">


        <div class="col-sm-9">

